æ˜ç™½ï¼Œæˆ‘å¹«ä½ æ”¹å¯«ä¹‹å‰çš„æ•´åˆç‰ˆï¼Œå®Œå…¨ç§»é™¤æœ¬åœ° /Account/Loginï¼Œæ”¹æˆç›´æ¥å°å‘ç¬¬ä¸‰æ–¹ SSO Login URLï¼ŒåŒæ™‚ä¿ç•™ ReturnUrl + 403 è‡ªå‹•å°å‘ï¼Œå…¨åŸŸå¥—ç”¨ã€‚

1ï¸âƒ£ è‡ªè¨‚ ActionFilter + AuthorizeAttribute
using System;
using System.Web;
using System.Web.Mvc;

public class SSOAuthorizeAttribute : AuthorizeAttribute
{
    // ç¬¬ä¸‰æ–¹ SSO ç™»å…¥ URL
    public string SsoLoginUrl { get; set; } = "https://sso.company.com/login";

    public override void OnAuthorization(AuthorizationContext filterContext)
    {
        var session = filterContext.HttpContext.Session;

        // å¦‚æœå·²ç™»å…¥å°±æ”¾è¡Œ
        if (session["User"] != null)
            return;

        RedirectToSso(filterContext);
    }

    protected override void HandleUnauthorizedRequest(AuthorizationContext filterContext)
    {
        RedirectToSso(filterContext);
    }

    public override void OnActionExecuted(ActionExecutedContext filterContext)
    {
        // å¦‚æœ Action è¿”å› 403ï¼Œçµ±ä¸€å°å‘ SSO Login
        if (filterContext.Result is HttpStatusCodeResult httpResult && httpResult.StatusCode == 403)
        {
            RedirectToSso(filterContext);
        }

        base.OnActionExecuted(filterContext);
    }

    private void RedirectToSso(ControllerContext filterContext)
    {
        string currentUrl = filterContext.HttpContext.Request.RawUrl;

        // é¿å… redirect loop
        if (!currentUrl.Contains("sso", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
        {
            string redirectUrl = $"{SsoLoginUrl}?ReturnUrl={HttpUtility.UrlEncode(currentUrl)}";
            filterContext.Result = new RedirectResult(redirectUrl);
        }
    }
}

2ï¸âƒ£ SSO Moduleï¼ˆè™•ç† Token / Sessionï¼‰
using System;
using System.Web;

public class SSOAuthModule : IHttpModule
{
    public void Init(HttpApplication context)
    {
        context.AuthenticateRequest += OnAuthenticateRequest;
        context.EndRequest += OnEndRequest;
    }

    private void OnAuthenticateRequest(object sender, EventArgs e)
    {
        var app = (HttpApplication)sender;
        var ctx = app.Context;

        // ç¬¬ä¸‰æ–¹ SSO ç™»å…¥æˆåŠŸå¾Œæœƒå¸¶ token
        var token = ctx.Request.QueryString["token"];
        if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(token))
        {
            // é©—è­‰ token å¾Œå»ºç«‹ Session
            ctx.Session["User"] = token;
        }
    }

    private void OnEndRequest(object sender, EventArgs e)
    {
        var app = (HttpApplication)sender;

        if (app.Response.StatusCode == 403)
        {
            string returnUrl = HttpUtility.UrlEncode(app.Request.RawUrl);
            if (!app.Request.RawUrl.Contains("sso", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
            {
                app.Response.Clear();
                app.Response.Redirect($"https://sso.company.com/login?ReturnUrl={returnUrl}", true);
            }
        }
    }

    public void Dispose() { }
}

Web.config è¨»å†Š Module
<system.webServer>
  <modules>
    <add name="SSOAuthModule" type="SSOAuthModule" />
  </modules>
</system.webServer>

